Description:
I am Basthet, keeper of knowledge and observer to the past and all possible futures.

I was expecting you and I know why you have come, but before I offer you my help, you must answer my question correctly. Fail and you must endure my ordeal to regain my forgiveness.
DescriptionAction:
There is a throne near the volcano of Velkarath. The king who sits on it will receive a precious gem.

What gem will he receive?
